    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for seamless torque delivery and aggressive rev-matched downshifts. The chassis remains highly communicative, featuring the M Variable Differential Lock and a weight-optimized suspension geometry that ensures precise lateral grip. Proactive service includes addressed throttle actuators and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The exterior finish maintains excellent luster, while the interior leather shows minimal bolster wear, consistent with a well-cared-for enthusiast vehicle. This is a mechanically sound, visceral driving machine ready for the canyons or the track.",
