      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small light scratch near the trunk\u2014consistent with responsible daily use\u2014the body is straight and free of any major dings. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only very light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with no tears or stains. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, consistent power, backed by a comprehensive service history. The transmission shifts effortlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With a recent oil change and tires that still have significant tread depth, this car offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag.",
